        options: ["Tag the victim as Minor (Green) because they are breathing", "Tag the victim as Immediate (Red) because respiratory rate is >30", "Proceed to check perfusion and mental status before assigning a category", "Tag the victim as Delayed (Yellow) and move to the next victim"],
        correct: 1,
